                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Dear Team,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we are trying to build lustre from source with ofed support.&lt;br/&gt;
But we didn&apos;t get success.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Always getting error while loading module lustre&lt;br/&gt;
modprobe  lustre&lt;br/&gt;
insmod /lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/lvfs.ko&lt;br/&gt;
insmod /lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/obdclass.ko&lt;br/&gt;
insmod /lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/ptlrpc.ko&lt;br/&gt;
WARNING: Error inserting ptlrpc (/lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/ptlrpc.ko): Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
WARNING: Error inserting fid (/lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/fid.ko): Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
WARNING: Error inserting mdc (/lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/mdc.ko): Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
WARNING: Error inserting osc (/lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/osc.ko): Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
WARNING: Error inserting lov (/lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/lov.ko): Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
FATAL: Error inserting lustre (/lib/modules/2.6.32-431.17.1.el6.x86_64/weak-updates/kernel/fs/lustre/lustre.ko): Input/output error&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need to understand, were we can look for correct or avoid this type of error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please reply us.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank You&lt;br/&gt;
Atul Yadav&lt;/p&gt;</description>
